    <item>
      <title>若出现竞争对手，MBK 或考虑提高对韩国锌业的收购报价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/mbk-to-consider-higher-offer-for-korea-zinc-if-rival-bids-emerge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私募股权公司 MBK Partners 的一位高管表示，如果有竞争对手竞购全球最大的精炼锌和铅生产商韩国锌业公司 (Korea Zinc Co.)，MBK Partners 愿意考虑提出更高的报价以控制该公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/mbk-to-consider-higher-offer-for-korea-zinc-if-rival-bids-emerge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 06:10:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本首相石破茂承诺将于十月提前举行大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/japan-s-ishiba-taps-veterans-for-cabinet-as-early-election-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本新领导人石破茂表示，如果他在周二被确认为日本新任首相，他将利用公众对他在上周执政的自民党总裁选举中获胜的积极反应，于 10 月 27 日举行全国大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/japan-s-ishiba-taps-veterans-for-cabinet-as-early-election-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 02:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市创 2008 年以来最大涨幅，有望进入牛市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/chinese-stocks-head-for-bull-market-as-property-rescue-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市延续了历史上最引人注目的逆转之一，连续第九天飙升，因为政府的刺激措施吸引投资者重返这个全球受创最严重的市场之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/chinese-stocks-head-for-bull-market-as-property-rescue-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 01:35:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>野村因违反规定被禁止参与多项日元债券交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/nomura-excluded-from-several-bond-underwritings-on-rule-breach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当局发现野村控股公司违反市场规则，该公司被排除在多笔日元债券交易的主承销商之列，这是日本公司今年第二次因违规而取消承销商资格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/nomura-excluded-from-several-bond-underwritings-on-rule-breach</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 00:14:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石破天惊的胜利导致日本股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-29/japan-stocks-set-to-fall-on-rate-hike-fears-after-ishiba-s-win-m1o64rpr</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石破茂在执政党总裁选举中意外击败高市早苗，令原本押注其竞争对手将出台更多货币刺激措施带来提振的投资者措手不及，日本股市随之大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-29/japan-stocks-set-to-fall-on-rate-hike-fears-after-ishiba-s-win-m1o64rpr</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 22:44:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员评估中东风险和中国刺激措施推动油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-30</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列击毙真主党领导人哈桑·纳斯鲁拉 (Hassan Nasrallah) 导致地区紧张局势加剧，且投资者预期中国将采取措施支持这一最大原油进口国的经济，油价随之上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-30</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 22:06:20 GMT</pubDate>
